; StreamLib Deno SDK — resolved from the static registry's npm mount by version
; (@tatolab scope). Reads are anonymous (tokenless). This is the first-party
; default; to resolve from a local static tree instead, run
; `streamlib registry use <tree>` (it rewrites this scope) or point it at the
; served mount, e.g. @tatolab:registry=http://127.0.0.1:8799/npm/.
; See docs/architecture/static-registry.md.
@tatolab:registry=https://registry.tatolab.com/npm/
